name: SwearJar2.0
tagline: SwearJar redefined for a good cause #BattleHack
body:
# SwearJar2.0 for BattleHack Chicago 2015.
Our app is SwearJar with a twist. It allows you to challenge your friends and help them reduce swearing and at the same time donate the money collected in the jar to charity.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
